'''硒酸锆'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Zr(SeO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>。它的四水合物可由[[硒酸|硒酸]]和[[氧氯化锆|氧氯化锆]]八水合物的饱和水溶液（或[[氢氧化锆|氢氧化锆]]<ref name=Nabar>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Applied Crystallography|volume=11|issue=1|issn=0021-8898|date=1978-02-01|pages=56–57|doi=10.1107/S0021889878012686|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0021889878012686|title=Studies on selenates. III. Crystal chemical data for zirconium and cerium selenate tetrahydrates|accessdate=2020-11-28|author=M. A. Nabar, V. R. Ajgaonkar|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603083007/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0021889878012686|dead-url=no}}</ref>）反应得到。四水合物属正交晶系，与[[硫酸锆|Zr(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·4H<sub>2</sub>O]]同构，它加热时失水，并于580 °C得到无水物。<ref>Davidovich, R. L.; Medkov, M. A. Zirconium and hafnium diselenates. ''Koordinatsionnaya Khimiya'', 1975. (1) 11: 1478-1480. ISSN: 0132-344X.</ref>它和[[氟化钾|氟化钾]]反应，可以得到K<sub>2</sub>Zr(SeO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>F<sub>2</sub>·3H<sub>2</sub>O.<ref>Davidovich, R. L.; Medkov, M. A. Selenatofluoride complex compounds of zirconium and hafnium. ''Koordinatsionnaya Khimiya'', 1975. 1 (12): 1646-1653. ISSN: 0132-344X.</ref>

